|1 |└─HASH GROUP BY      |        |2       |894         |
|2 |  └─MERGE JOIN       |        |96      |882         |
|3 |    ├─TABLE FULL SCAN|lineitem|96      |763         |
|4 |    └─TABLE FULL SCAN|orders  |3000    |93          |
=========================================================
